Title: You Go to My Head
Plot: At a fundraising gala at an estate, Edward offers a large sum if Rodrigo will play the violin. Rodrigo ups the ante and turns the tables. Hailey runs into Lizzie, and discovers her roommate has been hiding her upper crust roots -- before spending the rest of the night impressing a man with aristocratic credentials of his own.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
